title: Matsuricon 2009 Audio
description:
This is the complete audio of the Matsuricon 2009 dance.

Matsuricon is an Anime/Japanese culture convention located in Worthington, OH.

For more information on the event please check out http://matsuricon.org

This selection of music includes a huge variety of dance/trance/electronic/house/D&B/remixes etc.

The entire length is almost 5 hours of audio.

All audio is high quality MP3 mastered with Adobe Soundbooth.
